{"tid":1475081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣][素材]誰最暴力？","createTime":"2019-08-15T11:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T11:10:35.000Z","uid":265195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"19fe36c50e301c6e0466308baf351ced1692bdfa","tid":1475081,"uid":265195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:09:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dujBRGZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdujBRGZ.jpg&h=e8a1888f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5rAnOG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5rAnOG.jpg&h=5a09cbdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雙面文宣，由於有血腥畫面，所以個idea係第一頁向外摺埋派比人(可以釘埋/膠紙痴住)，印彩色比較震撼，可以嚇死班藍絲。<br />\n<br />\n其實我擔心818嘅遊行人數，喺連登以外，尤其是我身邊嘅中年淺黃/中立，佢地比起616出嚟遊行嘅意慾降低左，因為擔心安全、比鬼搞亂、出解放軍。大家整文宣嘅時候盡量脫離同溫層，target下啲中立、淺藍、中坑呀，因為依班人佔香港最多。"},{"pid":"51ded72ead2ba398861bfae89990af7ad00c2976","tid":1475081,"uid":265195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:09:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360884b1ea501992f0463a8acc36fa2a882a963b","tid":1475081,"uid":265195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77224f5f64a2845b5a6c2207286cd565df476dd3","tid":1475081,"uid":265195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a91d3838e1d8f064448ffb4d1930da5b44368c4","tid":1475081,"uid":265195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146b217d49cba9c2f8bda0037ddfed6e6c284e87","tid":1475081,"uid":265195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/